        <profileDesc>
            <creation/>
            <abstract>
                <p>A short text predicting different events, mostly of unfortunate character, that will ensue depending on the day of the week on which
                    the feast day of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS5741Johnthe">St John the Baptist</persName> falls. This work is attested independently as additional content, and as part of 
                    <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5048Hassabat">Ḥassābāt</ref>.</p>
            </abstract>
